The '''Cejansiji''' were natives of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Cejansij]]. They prided themselves on their [[Engineer/Legends|engineering]] skills. Among their civil engineering achievements was the [[Canyonade]], a multi-level [[City/Legends|city]] built into a [[canyon]] with numerous parks, [[Meditation/Legends|meditation]] [[Garden/Legends|gardens]], and skyarches.<ref name="SotP">''[[Specter of the Past]]''</ref>

The Cejansiji also had a tradition of peaceful political protests. During the [[Caamas Document]] crisis of [[19 ABY/Legends|19 ABY]], one such demonstration was witnessed by [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] and the [[Rellarin]] [[New Republic Observer]] [[Moshene Tre]]. This protest was a memorial for many of the victimized peoples of [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]], including the [[Caamasi/Legends|Caamasi]] and the [[Vrassh]].<ref name="SotP" />

